        Send an agreement out for signature to multiple recipients. Each recipient will receive and sign their own copy of the agreement. This is a primary endpoint which is used to create a new megaSign. A megaSign can be created using transientDocument, libraryDocument or a URL. You can create a megaSign in <b>IN_PROCESS</b> - Create a megaSign in this state to immediately send it. You can use the PUT/megaSigns/{megaSignId}/state endpoint to transition the state of megaSign. An allowed transition would follow the following sequence: IN_PROCESS -> CANCELLED.

        callback - The callback to be executed when the API call finishes
        Returns:
        The request call
        Throws:
        ApiException - If fail to process the API call, e.g. serializing the request body object
